                <tr>
                    <td width="15%">Date of Reg.</td>
                    <td width="15%"></td>
                    <td width="30%">DD / BC/ NEFTI FVG.</td>
                    <td width="40%"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td width="15%">Amount to be released</td>
                    <td width="15%">{!totalPendingAmountStr}</td>
                    <td width="30%">DD Payable at / IFSC Code &amp; Alc No.</td>
                    <td width="40%"></td>
                </tr>
            </table><br/>
            <div>
                2. Kindly release amount due for disbursement as per work progress certificate / as an advance of Rs.    for purchase of materials to my SB account mentioned above.
            </div><br/>
            <b>* Please also recover Interest and Insurance premium amount due from my SB Alc.</b>
            <br/>
